reviews.review_text: What the Hell I stumbled on this show while looking for versions of I Will Take You Home followed by Drums.  This is top notch.

Nice matrix This has a great sound/mix. I truly enjoyed this show from the beginning through the encore. The band sounds great! Also, I liked hearing something that I had never before heard--Hey Pockey Way. Cool tune.

Moreover, today is my Honey Bear's birthday--so that makes this show even more special to me.

Happy Birthday, Tracy!
I can't stand the rain Most likely my second favorite LL RAIN....Buffalo 89 stands out..
great drums I was at these shows and remember thinking that the drumming was fantastic. Upon hearing this show again 25 years later it turns out i was right. The drums on Pocky Way are just great.
